org.hps.record.scalers

Class ScalerData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.scalers.ScalerData

  • public final class ScalerData
extends Object
    This class encapsulates EVIO scaler data which is simply an array of integer values. The exact meaning of each of these integer words is defined externally to this class.
